          "subtype": "message",
          "text": "Perfect! I've completed the search and created `/workspace/implementors.json` with all concrete implementations of the `AggregatedDiscoveryServiceServer` gRPC interface. Here's a summary of what I found:\n\n## Results Summary\n\n### **envoyproxy/go-control-plane** (1 implementation)\n- **`server`** struct in `pkg/server/v3/server.go` - The main xDS server implementation from the go-control-plane library. Implements both `StreamAggregatedResources` and `DeltaAggregatedResources` methods.\n\n### **istio/istio** (4 implementations)\n1. **`DiscoveryServer`** struct in `pilot/pkg/xds/ads.go` - Istio's Pilot xDS server. Implements both ADS methods for the main control plane.\n\n2. **`testAdscRunServer`** struct in `pkg/adsc/adsc_test.go` - Test mock server for ADSC (ADS client simulator) testing. Implements both methods.\n\n3. **`mockDeltaXdsServer`** struct in `pkg/adsc/delta_test.go` - Test mock server specifically for Delta xDS testing. Implements both methods.\n\n4. **`XdsProxy`** struct in `pkg/istio-agent/xds_proxy.go` - The Istio agent's xDS proxy that relays xDS streams between Envoy and the control plane. Implements both methods with `StreamAggregatedResources` in `xds_proxy.go` and `DeltaAggregatedResources` in `xds_proxy_delta.go`.\n\n### **emissary-ingress/emissary**\nNo custom implementations found. Emissary uses the `server` type from go-control-plane via `ecp_v3_server.Server` in both `pkg/ambex/main.go` and `pkg/envoytest/controller.go`.\n\nAll results have been written to `/workspace/implementors.json` in the requested format.",
